title: Nami club
body:
Hello everyone, My name is saya, i'm play lol for 12 months now and really enjoy nami i'm currently ranking platinum 5 and i'm own a club called namis r us,
i'm looking for all nami mains from bronze-challenger ranking means nothing but i'm really want to have as many nami players together because no one is showing love for my most loved champion anymore My game name is SayaRose feel free to add and message me but nami must be in your top 3 played champions thank you to who is read this ♥
